# JavaScript lowering

HIR-to-JS and JS runtime semantics.

## Contract

- Input: validated HIR and companion metadata
- Output: JavaScript code and referenced external-function metadata
- Decides: JS runtime helper selection, bundle composition, external glue generation
- Must not decide: frontend semantics, HTML route assembly
- Invariant: JS lowering preserves Beanstalk semantics even when JavaScript has different native behavior

## Main paths

- `src/backends/js/`
- `src/projects/html_project/js_path.rs`

